user.biography: We are Mebie Baby! We offer modern + simple designed Swaddle Blankets and Baby basics.  collabs@mebiebaby.com #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 20, 2021.

node.text: We could put together matching gift sets all day! I love seeing the orders you all come up with and it’s always fun to mix and match items in the shop. #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and baby.

node.text: Do you prefer a gown or footie for a new baby? #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 18, 2021.

node.text: Three of our favorite neutral stretch gowns! We will be getting our fall items in the next week or two. The delays have been terrible but the end is in sight! Yay! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and baby.

node.text: These colors together are too good! Blue horizon + Rust. Do you prefer matching or contrasting? #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BABY'.

node.text: Such a cute gift set! Our accessories are fun to add to gifts and always needed. Burp cloths and bibs especially! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, baby and indoor.

node.text: Happy Saturday! I hope you all spend your weekend doing something fun. It’s feeling like summer is nearing to an end! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 13, 2021.

node.text: Some of our favorite gender neutral footie options! Which is your favorite? #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, baby and indoor.

node.text: These stretch gowns are one of my favorite must have items for the first couple months with baby! They are made out of a buttery soft fabric, the same as our stretch swaddles. #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 11, 2021 tagging @shopdeergrace.

node.text: The name suggestions were so fun! Now let’s do girl names for anyone to come look back on. What are you’re favorite girl names? #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and baby.

node.text: Who has loved these waffle quilts? I have this exact one set aside for baby because these are amazing! So soft, buttery and thick! The next time we restock them, we might be adding a new color to the collection. Any guesses? #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on August 09, 2021.

node.text:
Drop your favorite boy names below. 
Im expecting a boy in January and were having the hardest time thinking of a name! We will do the same for girl names this week also. #mebiebaby
